<div>
<p begin="00:00:00.000" end="00:00:04.760" style="s2">I&#39;m here in the UK at Penguin which I love because</p>
<p begin="00:00:04.760" end="00:00:08.300" style="s2"> I think Penguin is the best publisher in the world</p>
<p begin="00:00:08.720" end="00:00:10.900" style="s2"> and England is the center of the English language.</p>
<p begin="00:00:11.060" end="00:00:12.740" style="s2"> And that&#39;s quite a bit because</p>
<p begin="00:00:13.000" end="00:00:15.220" style="s2"> England has brought a tradition to the world</p>
<p begin="00:00:15.420" end="00:00:18.280" style="s2"> of truth-finding and clarification</p>
<p begin="00:00:18.400" end="00:00:21.440" style="s2"> and illuminated it in various ways</p>
<p begin="00:00:21.445" end="00:00:23.095" style="s2"> and I hope this book</p>
<p begin="00:00:23.380" end="00:00:28.560" style="s2"> that takes English tradition a step further</p>
<p begin="00:00:28.560" end="00:00:30.900" style="s2"> as befits a good settler.</p>
<p begin="00:00:31.280" end="00:00:32.280" style="s2"> So</p>
<p begin="00:00:32.720" end="00:00:35.140" style="s2"> I hope you read it</p>
<p begin="00:00:35.220" end="00:00:38.760" style="s2"> and I hope it helps put your life in order.</p>
<p begin="00:00:38.815" end="00:00:41.405" style="s2"> I think people like the things I&#39;ve said</p>
<p begin="00:00:41.405" end="00:00:43.025" style="s2"> very helpful in that area</p>
<p begin="00:00:43.380" end="00:00:45.980" style="s2"> and I have tried to clear them</p>
<p begin="00:00:46.180" end="00:00:48.180" style="s2"> and expand with this book</p>
<p begin="00:00:48.340" end="00:00:50.700" style="s2"> to deepen them.</p>
<p begin="00:00:50.920" end="00:00:53.340" style="s2"> So hopefully you will find out when you read it.</p>
</div>
